y school that belonged to that church and so I grew up very comfortable with the idea of being different.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1936, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my school\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1839}, {\"ngram\": \"that church\", \"from\": 1857, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"the idea\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1916}]}, {\"sentence\": \"... You get used to it.\", \"from\": 1937, \"to\": 1960, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I think if you are different in important ways, that can make a difference in your life.\\\"\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2050, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"important ways\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"a difference\", \"from\": 2023, \"to\": 2035}, {\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2048}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His father \\\"did not worry about what other people thought.\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2110, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His father\", \"from\": 2052, \"to\": 2062}, {\"ngram\": \"other people\", \"from\": 2089, \"to\": 2101}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He had hisown values and perspectives,\\\" an example Romney said he's followed.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2162, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitt_Romney\", \"score\": 0.9997663971539686, \"rank\": 0.00023354195848280423, \"text\": \"Romney\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitt_Romney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitt_Romney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hisown values\", \"from\": 2118, \"to\": 2131}, {\"ngram\": \"perspectives\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2148}, {\"ngram\": \"an example\", \"from\": 2151, \"to\": 2161}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"While we are all interested in whether we are popular and whether people like us and whether they agree with us, I think I am a little more comfortable with being, if you will, out on a ledge myself than perhaps the average politician.\\\"\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2426, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2256, \"to\": 2262}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2270}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2301}, {\"ngram\": \"a ledge\", \"from\": 2374, \"to\": 2381}, {\"ngram\": \"perhaps the average politician\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One such move was taking over the organization of the2002 Winter Gamesamid fallout from an international bribery scandal.\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2549, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One such move\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2441}, {\"ngram\": \"the organization\", \"from\": 2458, \"to\": 2474}, {\"ngram\": \"the2002 Winter Gamesamid fallout\", \"from\": 2478, \"to\": 2510}, {\"ngram\": \"an international bribery scandal\", \"from\": 2516, \"to\": 2548}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Romney said his initial reaction when his wife told him Utah wanted him to take the job was, \\\"That's ridiculous.\", \"from\": 2550, \"to\": 2662, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2550, \"end\": 2556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitt_Romney\", \"score\": 0.9997663971539686, \"rank\": 0.00023354195848280423, \"text\": \"Romney\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitt_Romney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitt_Romney\"}, {\"begin\": 2606, \"end\": 2610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"score\": 0.999999976364052, \"rank\": 1.3318757979403931e-08, \"text\": \"Utah\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Utah\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his initial reaction\", \"from\": 2562, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"his wife\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 2630, \"to\": 2637}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of course I am not going to do that.\\\"\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2700, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But over time, he said Ann Romney changed his mind, persuading him that the Olympics need to thrive as \\\"the last great stage on the public arena, where young people were able to see the greatest qualities of humanity, dedication, team work, determination, hard work.\\\"\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2969, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2725, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ann_Romney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ann Romney\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ann_Romney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ann_Romney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2711, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"his mind\", \"from\": 2744, \"to\": 2752}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2774, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"the last great stage\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2826}, {\"ngram\": \"the public arena\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"young people\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 2866}, {\"ngram\": \"the greatest qualities\", \"from\": 2884, \"to\": 2906}, {\"ngram\": \"humanity\", \"from\": 2910, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"dedication\", \"from\": 2920, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"team work\", \"from\": 2932, \"to\": 2941}, {\"ngram\": \"determination\", \"from\": 2943, \"to\": 2956}, {\"ngram\": \"hard work\", \"from\": 2958, \"to\": 2967}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also showed him that leading the Salt Lake Games \\\"was something I desperately needed, that my life up until that point professionally had been focused on being successful and making more money, but that ultimately was not going to be fulfilling.\", \"from\": 2971, \"to\": 3220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Salt Lake Games\", \"from\": 3004, \"to\": 3023}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 3029, \"to\": 3038}, {\"ngram\